<li><a href="/wiki/Expedition_of_Abu_Qatadah_ibn_Rab%27i_al-Ansari_(Khadirah)" title="Expedition of Abu Qatadah ibn Rab'i al-Ansari (Khadirah)">Khadirah</a></li>
